South Africa Must Spend $29 Billion on Aircraft, Bus. Day Says

-- B y   H i l t o n   S h o n e
-- 
2011-10-17T11:27:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/south-africa-must-spend-29-billion-on-aircraft-bus-day-says.html
South Africa  will need to spend $29
billion on new passenger jets over the next 20 years to meet
growing demand for  air travel ,  Business Day  reported, citing the
Airbus Global Market Forecast.  To contact the reporter on this story:
